{"tid":2234381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士地獄修煉記","createTime":"2020-10-08T00:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T01:25:42.000Z","uid":335440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5aba361250a18d6bbe152dc87d72cade08625a3b","tid":2234381,"uid":335440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟要返8半<br />\n咁我6點半起身之後搞掂晒啲嘢（刷牙洗臉個啲）<br />\n7點鐘就出門口<br />\n住得偏要行半個鐘先到巴士站<br />\n咁我就行行行<br />\n得返800米左右個陣發現得返幾分鐘巴士就開<br />\n嚇到我即刻狗沖咁跑去巴士站（帶著口罩）<br />\n好彩趕得切上車（辛苦到肺都爆）<br />\n咁以為上到車就冇事啦<br />\n點知道佢老母個仔成半個鐘先行得5個站<br />\n距離我目的地仲有成30幾個站<br />\n呢一刻我就知道肯定遲到<br />\n遲就遲啦 都冇辦法<br />\n問題係隔離個細佬嘈到成車都聽到<br />\n成個鐘冇停過<br />\n依家既心情係想拎起巴士個錘仔<br />\n敲爆佢塊玻璃跳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦我唔講啦<br />\n訓返半個鐘9點應該到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps：個細佬仲未落車"},{"pid":"3da9e91022658a91d08d583e979e6ed94a41e633","tid":2234381,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"多謝笑話一則"},{"pid":"19359563c9cb87fe6759553f703998ce14e6f09b","tid":2234381,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"住得偏要行半個鐘先到巴士站<br />\n<br />\n偏到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a28de2ff447c432f8c2e0cfaba959f128aba1f1","tid":2234381,"uid":335440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19359563c9cb87fe6759553f703998ce14e6f09b","tid":2234381,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"住得偏要行半個鐘先到巴士站<br />\n<br />\n偏到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:02:45.000Z","msg":"新界人"},{"pid":"254cb89b9aa05d0d9f3acf1d2be2bd22fed6d18a","tid":2234381,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a28de2ff447c432f8c2e0cfaba959f128aba1f1","tid":2234381,"uid":335440,"like":0,"dislike":0